-# Knowledge Card: Languages
-# border-info: Matches the blue color scheme generally associated with info/code
.card.border-0.shadow-sm.border-start.border-4.border-info
  .card-body.p-4
    
    -# --- Header ---
    .d-flex.align-items-center.mb-4
      .bg-info-subtle.text-info-emphasis.rounded-circle.d-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center.me-3.lh-1{style: "width: 48px; height: 48px"}
        %span.mi.md-24.fill code
      
      %div
        %h5.fw-bold.text-dark.mb-0 Programming Languages
        %small.text-secondary Configure available languages for submissions.

    -# --- Content Grid ---
    .row.g-4
      
      / 1. Source Code
      .col-lg-6.col-xxl-4
        .d-flex.gap-3
          / Icon
          .text-info.flex-shrink-0
            %span.mi.md-24 terminal
          
          %div
            %h6.fw-bold.text-dark.mb-1 Compilation
            %p.small.text-muted.mb-0.lh-sm
              Define how source code is compiled and executed. 
              Extensions determine which language is selected for a file.

      / 2. Extensions
      .col-lg-6.col-xxl-4
        .d-flex.gap-3
          .text-info.flex-shrink-0
            %span.mi.md-24 extension
          
          %div
            %h6.fw-bold.text-dark.mb-1 Extensions
            %p.small.text-muted.mb-0.lh-sm
              <strong>Default Ext:</strong> The primary extension.
              <br>
              <strong>Other Ext:</strong> Additional extensions (comma separated) that map to this language.

      / 3. System Languages
      .col-lg-6.col-xxl-4
        .d-flex.gap-3
          .text-info.flex-shrink-0
            %span.mi.md-24 lock
          
          %div
            %h6.fw-bold.text-dark.mb-1 System Languages
            %p.small.text-muted.mb-0.lh-sm
              Standard languages (ID < 20) are pre-configured and cannot be deleted or have their critical properties changed.
